SYNOPSIS
	Gossamer is a super simple PHP web application framework inspired by WSGI.

INSTALLATION
	Download the source.

EXAMPLE
	<?php

	require '/path/to/gossamer/Gossamer.php';

	class MainPage extends RequestHandler {
		public function get() {
			$this->response->setHeader('Content-Type', 'text/plain');
			$this->response->write('Hello world!');
		}
	}

	$app = new WsgiApplicationApp(array('/' => 'MainPage'));
	$app->run();


